<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=5.0">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0f1419">
    
    <!-- Performance optimizations -->
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="dark">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="dns-prefetch" href="//fonts.gstatic.com">
    
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/responsive-base.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/utilities.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .landing-page {
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(120, 119, 198, 0.3), transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(255, 119, 198, 0.3), transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 40% 80%, rgba(120, 219, 255, 0.3), transparent 50%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f23 0%, #010115 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #e5e7eb;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
        }
        
        /* Responsive hero */
        .hero-section {
            padding: var(--spacing-md);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .hero-content {
            padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(15, 20, 25, 0.95) 0%, rgba(20, 25, 35, 0.95) 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            border-radius: 24px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            box-shadow: 
                0 16px 64px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }
        
        .game-title {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        
        .game-subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
            color: #94a3b8;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        /* Feature grid */
        .game-features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: var(--spacing-lg);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .game-features {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: var(--spacing-md);
            }
        }
        
        .feature {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .feature:hover {
            border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .feature h3 {
            color: #10b981;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .feature p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        /* Action buttons */
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: var(--spacing-md);
            justify-content: center;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: stretch;
            }
            
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            min-width: 160px;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #047857);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #2563eb);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .game-info {
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
        }
        
        .info-section {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(15, 20, 25, 0.95) 0%, rgba(20, 25, 35, 0.95) 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 3rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            box-shadow: 
                0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }
        

    </style>
</head>
<body class="landing-page">
    <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 class="game-title">Aeturnis Online</h1>
            <p class="game-subtitle">A Text-Based MMORPG with Infinite Progression</p>
            <div class="game-features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>üó°Ô∏è Infinite Progression</h3>
                    <p>No level cap - grow your character forever with exponential scaling</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>üè∞ 8 Unique Races</h3>
                    <p>Choose from diverse races with meaningful stat bonuses and starting zones</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>‚öîÔ∏è Affinity System</h3>
                    <p>Master 7 weapon types and 8 magic schools through usage-based progression</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>üåç Turn-Based Combat</h3>
                    <p>Strategic combat with cooldowns, no button mashing required</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary">Create Account</a>
                <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-secondary">Login</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="game-info">
        <div class="info-section">
            <h2>Game Philosophy</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Infinite Progression:</strong> No level cap, endless growth</li>
                <li><strong>Racial Diversity:</strong> Meaningful racial choices affect gameplay</li>
                <li><strong>Affinity Depth:</strong> Complex mastery systems for weapons and magic</li>
                <li><strong>Community Focus:</strong> Social features and guild systems</li>
                <li><strong>Fair Play:</strong> No pay-to-win elements, skill-based progression</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-section">
            <h2>Choose Your Race</h2>
            <div class="race-preview">
                <div class="race-card">
                    <h4>Human</h4>
                    <p>Balanced and versatile - perfect for new players</p>
                </div>
                <div class="race-card">
                    <h4>Elf</h4>
                    <p>Magical affinity with high intelligence and wisdom</p>
                </div>
                <div class="race-card">
                    <h4>Dwarf</h4>
                    <p>Strong and hardy with excellent vitality</p>
                </div>
                <div class="race-card">
                    <h4>Orc</h4>
                    <p>Powerful warriors with incredible strength</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="game-footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Aeturnis Online. A classic text-based MMORPG experience.</p>
    </footer>
    
    <script src="/js/performance-utils.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/responsive-images.js"></script>
</body>
</html>